Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是不會對學妹心慈手軟的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然參加了 目標就是勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不會輸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.27,0:00:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的 我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說古蕾婭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.49,0:00:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽我說嘛 你是當真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哇 一望無際
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.16,0:01:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.62,0:01:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能在這麼美好的地方和古蕾婭獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.21,0:01:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這也太浪漫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.17,0:01:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說…說什麼呢 安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.20,0:01:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 美景已經看過了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.15,0:01:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.47,0:01:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.16,0:01:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走吧 就在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.17,0:01:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.83,0:01:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等著瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.58,0:01:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.98,0:02:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是已經走這麼遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說真的 能和古蕾婭獨處真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然非常開心…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哼哼哼！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哼！哼！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣很難走路的 安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就回去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就這樣回去 真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.54,0:02:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你摸哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.50,0:02:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才沒有摸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 說到底是你提出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼 今夜我們一起度過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.25,0:02:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽說星空會很美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們一起看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.26,0:02:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.52,0:02:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一起放煙火吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:02:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接著一起睡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的 啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.00,0:03:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我把那兩件一樣的睡衣帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行 絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就這麼定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡還不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:03:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你竟然知道這麼棒的地方 古蕾婭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.68,0:04:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡不會有別人打擾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下面 我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用沙子做城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭過來一起做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安也快把衣服脫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽話 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.31,0:04:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒什麼可是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼 古蕾婭幫我脫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你胡說什麼呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}挺厲害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這下 該開始了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.47,0:05:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開始什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}練習 是你要做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你說過 被別人知道太丟人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才會陪你來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.86,0:05:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來吧 把外衣脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安 不可以使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.41,0:06:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不用學會游泳也能在水面上行走的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吸 吸 呼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吸 吸 呼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別害怕 有我在的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.51,0:07:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是 腳下已經踩不到地面了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先試試靠自己漂浮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}漂浮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.14,0:07:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人生來就是不能漂浮的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事的 你試試
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來吧 安 慢慢吸口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}呼氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吸氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}呼氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再放鬆一些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很好 看著天空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手腳要放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}身體不能僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手腳放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放鬆…放鬆…放鬆…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}睜開眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原來浮在水面上是這個感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.39,0:10:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝 古蕾婭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Manaria Friends 第七話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}捉迷藏
Comment: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}---------------next------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是手持燃放的煙火嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽說是來自東方國度的煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:11:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}米蘭達老師為我們訂購的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會有危險吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會 放心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每次公主殿下這樣說總會做出一些危險的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明可以看見星星 還要放煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.76,0:12:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭的國家不會這麼做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一般不會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽說煙火自古就是用來慶祝喜慶之事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然要放煙火 不如用來攻擊別人更有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼我們開始吧
Comment: 0,0:13:27.04,0:13:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}#請勿模仿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭 接下來做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}煙火也放完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}煙火真好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想到明天要回去了 覺得有些不捨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.99,0:13:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過想做的事情都做了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只剩下一起睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.03,0:13:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我今天可努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.19,0:13:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是漫長的一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終於能穿上一樣的睡衣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好期待和你一起睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}絕對…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓我們一起迎接明天的美麗朝陽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}絕對不可以的
